    VectorTxtToTfProjectorTsv

    VectorTxtToW2v
    Converts a vector.txt file as written by this framework (in the format of GloVe vectors) to the classic word2vec format where the first line contains the number of elements and the dimension.
    WalkMerger
    Walk merger: By default, walks are written to various gzipped files.
